<item>
            <title>[SOLR-9062] TestDistributedStatsComponentCardinality OOM when ssl + clientAuth</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-9062</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t have a seed to share, but when hacking SolrTestCaseJ4 to force SSL+clientAuth in all tests, TestDistributedStatsComponentCardinality will reliably fail with an OOM.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12964735">SOLR-9062</key>
            <summary>TestDistributedStatsComponentCardinality OOM when ssl + clientAuth</summary>
