&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-9062&quot; title=&quot;TestDistributedStatsComponentCardinality OOM when ssl + clientAuth&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-9062&quot;&gt;SOLR-9062&lt;/a&gt;: SuppressSSL on TestDistributedStatsComponentCardinality for now since it causes OOM with default test heap sizes&lt;/p&gt;

